    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced for structural longevity. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and a perfectly calibrated M-variable limited-slip differential. Finished in its original factory paint with zero oxidation, the interior boasts Nappa leather with no bolster compression or pixel failure on the dash. A true turnkey performance icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
