    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This single-owner masterpiece has been pampered since day one, stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable soft-shell cover. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, protected by a multi-layer professional ceramic coating; you will find zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary that still carries the faint aroma of new premium leather. The seats show absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by original factory mats since delivery. Every button, switch, and digital display operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed at the original dealership. It has never been driven in inclement weather and has been strictly hand-washed using pH-neutral cleansers. This is an opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from one sitting on a showroom floor.",
